author: Source: Thetelegraphand Argus
title: Steven Finn heads home with foot injury, Chris Jordan steps in for England - Thetelegraphand Argus
text:
Steven Finn is to return home from England's Test tour of the United Arab Emirates, with a bone stress injury to his left foot, and will be replaced by Chris Jordan. Finn had made a late run into the reckoning for selection as third seamer for the ongoing first match of three against Pakistan, in Abu Dhabi, only to suffer pain in his foot.
 Thetelegraphand Argus.
